POSSIBLE CONSIDERATIONS FOR TEST FUNCTIONS?
===========================================
+ Segmented Selection
    - NONE (a default is declared in viewDidLoad)

+ Encode Button
    - Message Field
        > blank field
        > spaces
        > unseeable ascii characters
        > foreign characters
    - Secret Field
        > blank field
        > spaces
        > non-digit characters
        > foreign characters

+ Decrypt Button
    - Message Field
        > blank field
        > spaces
        > unseeable ascii characters
        > foreign characters
    - Secret Field
        > blank field
        > spaces
        > non-digit characters
        > foreign characters

+ Clear Button
    - Message Field
        > blank field
        > spaces
        > unseeable ascii characters
        > foreign characters
    - Secret Field
        > blank field
        > spaces
        > non-digit characters
        > foreign characters
    - Output
        > while an error is displayed in the output

+ Copy Button
    - Output
        > empty output
        > error output
        > filled fields + blank output
